Package teal.sim.spatial

Spatial objects do not have a physical 'body' but are used to represent field values and data visualizations.

Package teal.sim.spatial Description

Spatial objects do not have a physical 'body' but are used to represent field values and data visualizations. This sentence is here to prevent errors in javadoc generation.
